---
title: Peruvian Lomo Saltado Steak with Spiced Fries
description: Onions, fries, and steak are the perfect combination for a weeknight dinner!  This dish capitalizes on the classic pairing, adding spicy pickled jalapeños. Altogether, it's the perfect dish to pick you up at the end of a long day!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/peruvian-lomo-saltado-steak-6fdbf862.jpg
